package "P-Debug: src/testforge/debug/" as P_Debug {
  [DebugLogger] as DebugLogger
  note right of DebugLogger
    Singleton. configure(slug, output_dir, debug_mode).
    event(name, payload) → stderr + debug/debug.log.
    Sanitiza campos sensíveis (password/token/api_key/secret).
    Ativado por recording.debug_mode=True / --debug CLI.
  end note
}

package "P-Recording-BUG018: Recorder + RecorderOverlay (atualizado)" as P_RecBug018 {
  [Recorder] as Recorder
  note right of Recorder
    BrowserConfig.navigation_timeout_ms (padrão 60000 ms).
    Recorder.finish() verifica page.is_closed() antes de
    chamar FingerprintCollector.collect_final() — BUG-019.
    BrowserManager.close() envolvido em try/except — BUG-019.
    ScreenshotCollector.capture_screenshot() e
    DOMSnapshotCollector.capture_dom_snapshot() verificam
    page.is_closed() + try/except antes de chamar API
    Playwright — BUG-021.
  end note
  [RecorderOverlay_BUG018] as RecorderOverlay_BUG018
  note right of RecorderOverlay_BUG018
    OVERLAY_JS usa window.__tfRecordingActive (+ sessionStorage)
    para persistir estado entre full-page navigations — BUG-018.
    updateUI() chamado ao final da inicialização da IIFE para
    sincronizar statusEl.textContent com state restaurado — BUG-021.
    _event_queue: queue.Queue para comunicação thread-safe
    entre OVERLAY_JS e Python collect_step.
  end note
}

package "P-Node-Recording: collect_step (atualizado)" as P_NodeRec {
  [CollectStep] as CollectStep
  note right of CollectStep
    Pull-based: page.evaluate("window.__tfEventQueue.splice(0)").
    Loop 300×100ms. Pacing via time.sleep() (síncrono) — BUG-021
    (wait_for_timeout criava coroutines asyncio órfãs).
    Verifica page.is_closed() no início de cada
    iteração (BUG-019). DebugLogger instrumentado a cada 10 iter.
    Transição page.on("close") → finish_requested=True.
  end note
}

DebugLogger --> Recorder : instrumenta browser_launch
DebugLogger --> CollectStep : instrumenta collect_step_poll
DebugLogger --> RecorderOverlay_BUG018 : instrumenta overlay_event
Recorder --> RecorderOverlay_BUG018 : injeta OVERLAY_JS + page.on("close")
RecorderOverlay_BUG018 --> CollectStep : window.__tfEventQueue (pull-based)
CollectStep --> Recorder : finish_requested → Recorder.finish()

@enduml
